Source.Name: python-openpyxl
Source.Summary: A Python library to read/write Excel 2010 xlsx/xlsm files
Source.Description: openpyxl is a Python library to read/write Excel 2010 xlsx/xlsm/xltx/xltm files. It was born from lack of existing library to read/write natively from Python the Office Open XML format.
